On Dec 31, 2025, Optimism's development focused on expanding token listings with the addition of PAGE to Base and significant protocol adjustments, including the removal of L2OO support and setting a new default game type to CANNON_KONA. These updates reflect ongoing efforts to refine the Superchain ecosystem and enhance core protocol functionality.
